1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,720
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:55,932 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 2=

11
00:00:59,203 --> 00:01:02,640
(Ten Thousand Years Ago)

12
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,604
(Lin Ningxue, Holy Maiden)

13
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,200
After 300 years of seclusion,

14
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,959
I finally reached
the Heavenly God Realm.

15
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,560
I'm finally back.

16
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,695
(Su Wubing, Immortal King)

17
00:01:28,953 --> 00:01:32,891
♪Snow falls upon your sleeves♪

18
00:01:32,891 --> 00:01:37,651
♪Yet it cannot conceal
a fate-bound curse♪

19
00:01:37,651 --> 00:01:42,451
♪A thousand years of cultivation
were distilled into a single lamp♪

20
00:01:42,451 --> 00:01:47,291
♪Foolishly trying to light
the long night♪

21
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,760
Ningxue.

22
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:57,719
I did it.

23
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,640
I've reached the Heavenly God Realm.

24
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,719
From now on,

25
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:03,439
I'll break your curse.

26
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,959
No matter what it takes.

27
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:07,159
Break!

28
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:18,240
Ningxue.

29
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:20,400
Ningxue!

30
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:25,120
You, a lowly immortal, dare defy me.

31
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:30,240
Defy the Heavenly Dao?
Your soul shall return to the void.

32
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,479
The Heavenly Dao?

33
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:34,599
So the Heavenly Dao
actually curses people from birth

34
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,479
and kills them at such a young age?

35
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,199
Stubborn fool.

36
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:44,400
Ningxue!

37
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,919
No!

38
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:50,479
It wasn't easy for you
to reach the Heavenly God Realm.

39
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,800
Don't ruin it.

40
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,479
All my cultivation

41
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,120
is for her.

42
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,439
How is that ruining anything?

43
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:00,680
Sword, come!

44
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,400
Whether you're the Heavenly Dao
or a demon,

45
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:14,000
eat this!

46
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,039
If you want Ningxue,

47
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:19,039
step over my dead body first.

48
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,159
Even if my soul shatters,

49
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,719
I'll defy you to the end.

50
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:40,240
Even with Heavenly God Realm power
overwhelming,

51
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,520
Immortal King just ended seclusion.

52
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,120
Ningxue!

53
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,840
The Heavenly God Sword
isn't fully refined yet.

54
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:46,280
It may not be able
to stand against the Heavenly Dao.

55
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,319
Even if the Heavenly Dao won't allow it,

56
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:53,479
I swear to follow you forever.

57
00:03:56,677 --> 00:04:01,092
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

58
00:04:01,092 --> 00:04:05,844
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

59
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:12,159
The Holy Maiden's curse can actually
activate the Time-Space Array.

60
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,800
From the heavens above
to the underworld below,

61
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,839
I will never fail you.

62
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,360
Just you?

63
00:04:30,319 --> 00:04:32,079
This is spiritual power?

64
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:38,040
A low-level martial artist

65
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,639
like you can't cure

66
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:40,399
my father's illness.

67
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:41,720
Get out.

68
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,560
Get out!

69
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,399
- Welcome back, Miss.
- Welcome back, Miss.

70
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:27,040
How is my father?

71
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,920
Master, he...

72
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,120
It's still the same.

73
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,680
In this life,

74
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,519
her family is fairly well-off.

75
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,040
Tonight, without my permission,

76
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,839
no one is allowed to disturb my father.

77
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,519
Yes.

78
00:05:56,274 --> 00:05:57,795
(Yingying)

79
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:02,639
Hello.

80
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:03,920
Hello, Ningxue.

81
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,480
The person with you...

82
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,639
I knew.

83
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,920
He wasn't arranged by you.

84
00:06:08,759 --> 00:06:10,040
He wasn't,

85
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:11,959
but he's from our martial hall.

86
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,639
You know him?

87
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:15,959
Of course.

88
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,480
His name is Su Wubing.

89
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:18,879
His mother has been

90
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,079
seriously ill for years,

91
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,240
and they're very poor,

92
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,519
so I let him stay and do odd jobs.

93
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,439
And he can't even beat kids.

94
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:27,839
Basically useless...

95
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,759
Just an ordinary nobody.

96
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,519
How is that possible?

97
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,480
Alright, I got it, Yingying.

98
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:43,040
(A martial hall apprentice?)

99
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,680
(I wanna give it a try anyway.)

100
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,439
(I didn't expect)

101
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:13,319
(the curse is still clinging to you.)

102
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,639
What are you doing?

103
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:22,560
Stop spacing out.

104
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:23,639
Keep up.

105
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,839
(Only three months left.)

106
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,279
(In this life,)

107
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:33,160
(she's just a mortal.)

108
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,079
(She can't bear the curse anymore.)

109
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:43,120
Can you really cure my father?

110
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:43,920
Yes.

111
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:48,639
The Lin family's fate is in your hands.

112
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,600
(I'll save the Lin family,)

113
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,000
(and you, too.)

114
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,160
Come with me.

115
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,360
Dad,

116
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,920
I've found someone who can cure you.

117
00:08:09,048 --> 00:08:10,199
(Lin Rong, Head of Lin family)

118
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,399
(Lin Rong, Head of Lin family)
Xue,

119
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,680
my time has come.

120
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:16,959
Dad...

121
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:20,399
No. It won't happen.

122
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:23,519
The burden of our family

123
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:26,839
is all on you now.

124
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,720
After I'm gone,

125
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:33,679
the Gu family will
definitely move against us.

126
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:37,519
Take care of yourself.

127
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,159
Dad...

128
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,480
Dad, no.

129
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,240
You'll get better, you will.

130
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,840
(This is Abyss Poison.)

131
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,600
Stop!

132
00:09:37,697 --> 00:09:41,800
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

133
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:46,520
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

134
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:51,400
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

135
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:56,520
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

136
00:09:56,520 --> 00:10:00,920
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

137
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:05,600
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

138
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:11,000
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

139
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:17,027
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

